{
  "texts": [
    "We used gpt-4o-mini as the generative model.",
    "The top-5 retrieved chunks were used as input for the LLM, and generated answers were compared to groundtruth responses using semantic similarity measures.",
    "We reused the datasets from Section 3.2, as they included long documents, evidence, and reference answers.",
    "As mentioned earlier, we used three proxy tasks the study chunking.",
    "We cannot directly assess the quality of retrieval at the chunk level due to the lack of ground-truth at the chunk level."
  ]
}